{"tid":1002044,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啱先行年宵有個好有才嘅呀叔","createTime":"2019-01-30T15:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T02:29:45.000Z","uid":191239,"like":2408,"dislike":120,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"9e1793ec0968c44f848c074876295c12d2f54f88","tid":1002044,"uid":191239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"同女朋友行過一檔廿蚊全部都賣不銹鋼煮食用具嘅檔口 <br />\n<br />\n有個睇落五十零嘅呀叔駁住咪講 <br />\n<br />\n拿！喱把刀啲女朋友見你地條仔出去叫雞就啱曬啦！幾撚鋒利！（拎住把刀喺度切紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n跟住個呀叔指住後面，有個不銹鋼晾衫架 上面夾住全部都係五百蚊紙<br />\n<br />\n見唔見到後面呀？女朋友啲T-back同bra買喱啲衣夾夾住曬就啱晒架啦，佢如果跌落黎 張五百蚊當利是送比你又點話！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好少見啲咁嘅sales 行年宵又估唔到會有啲咁嘅檔口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸最後女朋友買左把刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764a788be8a961f56b9947fa235098d566516f96","tid":1002044,"uid":135278,"like":657,"dislike":1,"score":656,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T15:48:45.000Z","msg":"巴打 小心 保重 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e538557c9792c8171d13aef4c7bc1d9d95ee3cc1","tid":1002044,"uid":33439,"like":661,"dislike":21,"score":640,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T15:51:15.000Z","msg":"咩叫好有才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔明"},{"pid":"ea3d46e451a36d901a152fc8c57b5d40a7